{"tid":1507233,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"人大通過新修訂藥品管理法","createTime":"2019-08-26T05:23:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T05:26:41.000Z","uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"314d51a5f8509250a775ddd25b627dd066ba5800","tid":1507233,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:23:10.000Z","msg":"2019/08/26 13:20<br />\n在北京，全國人大常委會通過新修訂的藥品管理法，把未獲批准進口、但在境外合法的藥物帶回內地，不再按假藥論處。 <br />\n<br />\n在過往的藥品管理法中，一些在境外合法、並取得治療成效的新藥，如果在國內未批准進口，會被視為假藥，亦有個案因為幫病人代購印度仿製藥而被判刑。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新修訂的藥品管理法將這些藥物剔出假藥名單中，又單獨列出，如果未經批准、少量購買這些藥，情節較輕的可以減輕處罰或免於處罰，但全國人大法工委強調這樣並不代表合法化。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/555716/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A7%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%E6%96%B0%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82%E8%97%A5%E5%93%81%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E6%B3%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F555716%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2580%259A%25E9%2581%258E%25E6%2596%25B0%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E8%25A8%2582%25E8%2597%25A5%25E5%2593%2581%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E7%2590%2586%25E6%25B3%2595&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY9mOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=ed177e63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F555716%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2580%259A%25E9%2581%258E%25E6%2596%25B0%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E8%25A8%2582%25E8%2597%25A5%25E5%2593%2581%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E7%2590%2586%25E6%25B3%2595&h=1750f971\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/555716/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A7%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%E6%9